{"tid":2136162,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"將軍澳屋苑設計「走光浴室」 鄰居日日睇全相","createTime":"2020-08-02T02:53:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T17:08:55.000Z","uid":176553,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ce4758f46effca23034be06f59989e046259a496","tid":2136162,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DObOOB_TrlFoqh5ajbxQ5_uKalQ=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IUMLTTBU4TPUNWRGVKC6B5I7V4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDObOOB_TrlFoqh5ajbxQ5_uKalQ%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIUMLTTBU4TPUNWRGVKC6B5I7V4.jpg&h=ca6985fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_0fO2cmCDD386W3rbBwBDYLVomo=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VPKZTS3BTHY27SOG7LHL4RO3UA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_0fO2cmCDD386W3rbBwBDYLVomo%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVPKZTS3BTHY27SOG7LHL4RO3UA.jpg&h=12514757&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳一個新入伙屋苑，在部份單位的浴缸旁加設一幅近乎落地般大的磨砂玻璃，以增加單位的採光度。不過原來從屋外望進去，浴室磨砂玻璃頓變透光幕牆，住客站着沖涼頻演「走光浴」，有住戶希望屋苑發展商盡快杜塞漏洞及作出補救。《蘋果》發現該屋苑共9幢樓宇，至少有800戶出現「走光浴室」，有戶主得知後大表驚訝：「係男係女都睇得一清二楚！」專家提醒，千萬別貼近窗邊沖涼，因為越近會越清晰，建議加遮光紙或窗簾防走光。<br />\n<br />\n「日頭真係睇到9成，係睇到晒咁滯，除咗個樣睇唔到之外，身體啲部位係睇得好清吓㗎，如果係女士就會見到上身露點囉！」女住戶Rain每天看盡不少男女住戶的裸體，令她尷尬不已，「我都唔想睇，但係我個廳冇裝窗簾，所以都冇辦法！」她直言，其客廳與對面座單位的浴室，相距不足20米，幾乎是打對面，每晚樓上樓下的鄰居沖涼猶如一場場連環「出浴Live」。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200802/3XLMLLWUIR5ZNSCEFCM66HKA54\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200802%2F3XLMLLWUIR5ZNSCEFCM66HKA54&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnRR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=51bc1e3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200802%2F3XLMLLWUIR5ZNSCEFCM66HKA54&h=a8ff2c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200802/3XLMLLWUIR5ZNSCEFCM66HKA54</a>"},{"pid":"b5697c8c1c46b228477bbacbd6873eec1e31be63","tid":2136162,"uid":312363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:55:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601d030f815c28b81bda57b666003391bd3cecf9","tid":2136162,"uid":360603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T02:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d11a13451886d8e779a6a8db2210f06af69d0097","tid":2136162,"uid":16676,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"正喎<br />\n條啫有幾粗, 有幾長, 𥄫晒<br />\n<br />\n跪求無格版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da79b5f4f39ff164a3a78da7489e4aefce36be62","tid":2136162,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38eee5f9973061f9448575d28499bd1936e4a819","tid":2136162,"uid":7278,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T03:27:31.000Z","msg":"有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又見唔到樣"},{"pid":"08b6b19206948f52792d26294f43b5905605a85d","tid":2136162,"uid":140869,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"38eee5f9973061f9448575d